I"U<h1 class="align-to-center" id="le-maelström">LE MAELSTRÖM </h1>

<p class="align-to-center">A short lifestyle video ad collaboration between eco-tourism brand Buddha Ventura and <a href="http://havencreative.studio/">Haven creative studio</a> for <a href="https://lemaelstrom.ca/en/">Le Maelström</a> eco-luxe and sustainable cabins near Québec City. Capturing a unique above the clouds glamping experience at an altitude of 550 meters. With dramatic landscapes, solar-powered and gas-heated amenities the cozy breathtaking getaway experience at the Lagöm cabin lives up to its Swedish influence of not too much, not too little but <em>just enough</em>. </p>

